                      "name": "v3_p1",
                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Type IAA, IA, I, II and III. Each duty rating maps to a maximum working load and a use case. In this clip we walk through which rating applies to which job, so you choose with confidence on the first try. Remember: the load includes you, your clothing, tools, and anything you carry up the ladder.",
